" />"},{"pid":"f5c52ea158eeb39b1f7f76d4930330c2cf3dea26","tid":906287,"uid":136431,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T01:27:48.000Z","msg":"網民直斥：「那不是『你的』台灣，那是中國的台灣」<br />\n<br />\n唔係人哋嘅，咁係邊個嘅？<br />\n同隔籬屋吠，呢個唔係你屋企，係我屋企有咩分別<br />\n自己連人哋屋企鎖匙都冇，又未入過去，人哋又唔歡迎，屈人哋屋企係自己嘅，仲變態過玄牛收樓"},{"pid":"f99c78e1024fe66edd0d3698dc84d1ba6ca7d072","tid":906287,"uid":41500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T01:48:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>網民直斥：「那不是『你的』台灣，那是中國的台灣」</blockquote><br />\n幾時開始支國蝗自出自入台灣架 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eeffe98061d201c17df6279db0acf21faab567f7","tid":906287,"uid":17765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T01:59:12.000Z","msg":"明年內地電影人不要去了！<br />\n<br />\n去嘅死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44d617fd45e586b883abb399b90ec1dea0e7f94d","tid":906287,"uid":5715,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T03:16:15.000Z","msg":"成班奴隸鬧台灣，結果自己都無得睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真係比中國收番台灣又如何，奴隸仍然都係奴隸，唔知佢地鬧得咁興奮做咩"},{"pid":"1eee10722ead1c0d9cf3ae9bff82bc312511bfd2","tid":906287,"uid":167506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T05:54:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cd537246994946891ba3d93bc83b242b3266212","tid":906287,"uid":167506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T06:36:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80b1ac0b6ef23aa1f7e610f4a58dffa0de2cb377","tid":906287,"uid":71393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited